In the past, I approached this problem by establishing a `Model` type for every input that would hang onto a few interesting props—
```{
  value: T, 
  isTouched: boolean,
  errors: Array&lt;{id, display}&gt;,
  warnings: Array&lt;{id, display}&gt;,
  notes: Array&lt;{id, display}&gt;
}```

